She seems perfectly fine.

38
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:47,879
She's in a good mood
and her work isn't affected.

39
00:03:48,719 --> 00:03:50,638
She also didn't announce
to the world...

40
00:03:50,639 --> 00:03:51,639
that she's single again.

41
00:03:53,759 --> 00:03:54,800
Han Han.

42
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:57,319
There's something
I need to discuss with you.

43
00:03:58,680 --> 00:04:00,438
I've booked a flight
for early tomorrow.

44
00:04:00,439 --> 00:04:01,560
I have to rush back.

45
00:04:01,879 --> 00:04:02,918
Why?

46
00:04:02,919 --> 00:04:04,120
Aren't we staying for one more day?

47
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:07,039
There's a problem with Zeng Cheng.

48
00:04:07,439 --> 00:04:08,479
She needs me.

49
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:17,000
You know Zeng Cheng.

50
00:04:17,079 --> 00:04:18,120
You've met her too.

51
00:04:21,279 --> 00:04:22,879
But no one knows
what she's really like...

52
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:24,360
except me.

53
00:04:25,050 --> 00:04:26,120
What do you mean?

54
00:04:27,439 --> 00:04:30,480
Actually, Zeng Cheng
is very fragile and sensitive.

55
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:33,279
She has to keep up
appearances outside,

56
