which puts even more stress
on her privately.

57
00:04:36,639 --> 00:04:39,000
The divorce has hit her hard.

58
00:04:39,839 --> 00:04:41,879
She was crying
on the phone just now...

59
00:04:42,199 --> 00:04:43,319
and she was very emotional.

60
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:46,318
So I promised her
I'd go back to visit her.

61
00:04:46,319 --> 00:04:48,839
Who would have stable emotions
after a divorce?

62
00:04:50,199 --> 00:04:51,240
Han Han.

63
00:04:52,079 --> 00:04:53,729
When Zeng Cheng was in college,

64
00:04:53,730 --> 00:04:54,730
she suffered from bipolar disorder.

65
00:04:54,839 --> 00:04:56,199
She got better after treatment.

66
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:59,079
I'm worried that
the divorce will provoke her.

67
00:04:59,120 --> 00:05:00,878
If she relapses
and her health takes a hit,

68
00:05:00,879 --> 00:05:02,050
I'd feel very guilty.

69
00:05:03,170 --> 00:05:04,170
Han Han.

70
00:05:04,170 --> 00:05:05,170
Listen to me.

71
00:05:06,279 --> 00:05:08,120
You're the most sensible girl
I've ever met.

72
00:05:10,170 --> 00:05:11,519
Although Zeng Cheng
and I are separated,

73
00:05:11,959 --> 00:05:14,279
but we were married
for more than 10 years.

74
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:17,560
I can't just stand by
during her toughest times.

75
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:19,730
You can understand that, right?

76
00:05:19,959 --> 00:05:21,480
Haven't you made
your divorce public?

77
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:23,560
It can only be made public
when she feels it's appropriate.

78
00:05:23,610 --> 00:05:25,610
This was our agreement
during the divorce.

79
00:05:26,439 --> 00:05:28,278
She values her reputation a lot
and we have...

80
00:05:28,279 --> 00:05:29,720
- a common circle of friends.
- What about me?

81
00:05:32,199 --> 00:05:33,319
This is a different matter.

82
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:37,639
For her, it's about responsibility.

83
00:05:38,319 --> 00:05:39,839
For you, it's about feelings.

84
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:41,359
You know I love you.

85
00:05:41,360 --> 00:05:42,399
Even if it's not announced,

86
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:43,559
you can at least let her know...

87
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:44,719
