can't you?

88
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:45,720
No.

89
00:05:50,519 --> 00:05:52,639
When the time is right,
I'll tell her.

90
00:05:53,319 --> 00:05:55,759
Telling her now
will only provoke her.

91
00:05:55,839 --> 00:05:56,839
Right?

92
00:05:56,840 --> 00:05:57,879
