create trouble for ourselves?

94
00:06:02,959 --> 00:06:04,279
You saw her Moments, right?

95
00:06:05,199 --> 00:06:06,439
Why is she working so hard?

96
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:08,199
Taking the early flight out
and the late flight back.

97
00:06:09,759 --> 00:06:11,680
She just doesn't want
to face reality.

98
00:06:12,079 --> 00:06:13,319
It's nothing but avoidance.

99
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:15,000
She doesn't want to be alone.

100
00:06:16,839 --> 00:06:17,920
This situation...

101
00:06:18,439 --> 00:06:19,600
won't last long.

102
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:21,720
You have to trust me.

103
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,600
I know...

104
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:26,600
what I'm doing...

105
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:28,319
and my boundaries.

106
00:06:36,199 --> 00:06:37,240
I knew...

107
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:39,000
you'd understand me.

108
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:42,199
You certainly won't stoop...

109
00:06:44,680 --> 00:06:45,759
to such vulgar thoughts.

110
00:06:46,160 --> 00:06:47,480
Since you've put it that way,

111
00:06:47,839 --> 00:06:50,680
