I can't say them out loud.

112
00:06:53,839 --> 00:06:55,160
However, I have a condition.

113
00:06:56,279 --> 00:06:57,279
What is it?

114
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:58,600
When you visit her,

115
00:06:58,601 --> 00:07:00,000
you have to think of me
all the time.

116
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:01,199
Of course.

117
00:07:04,759 --> 00:07:06,480
The way you treat your ex-wife...

118
00:07:06,959 --> 00:07:08,839
shows that
you're a sentimental person.

119
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:13,680
Han Han.

120
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:15,439
You're the most
understanding girl...

121
00:07:16,680 --> 00:07:18,279
I've ever met.

122
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:22,480
I'm so lucky to have met you.

123
00:08:29,639 --> 00:08:30,680
Babe.

124
00:08:37,210 --> 00:08:38,279
Babe.

125
00:08:39,279 --> 00:08:40,360
Hello.

126
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:43,039
He Zhi Nan.

127
