128
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:46,840
He Zhi Nan.

129
00:08:47,330 --> 00:08:48,360
Babe.

130
00:08:56,210 --> 00:08:57,279
Hello?

131
00:08:57,330 --> 00:08:58,330
Lazy bum.

132
00:08:58,679 --> 00:09:00,090
Why aren't you up yet?

133
00:09:00,399 --> 00:09:02,090
I called you so many times,
but you didn't answer.

134
00:09:06,519 --> 00:09:07,639
What are your plans today?

135
00:09:10,919 --> 00:09:12,039
What plans can there be?

136
00:09:13,519 --> 00:09:15,240
I'll just stay home with my parents.

137
00:09:15,480 --> 00:09:16,759
What a surprise.

138
00:09:17,330 --> 00:09:20,360
You said you wouldn't spend
the whole weekend at home.

139
00:09:22,210 --> 00:09:23,210
It's my grandma's birthday...

140
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:25,279
next week.

141
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:32,329
Are you hiding something from me?

142
00:09:32,330 --> 00:09:33,399
No.

143
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:37,279
What makes you think so?

144
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:46,039
Nan Nan.

145
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:49,399
We just got together.

146
00:09:49,799 --> 00:09:50,879
What I like...

147
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:53,360
is your honesty and sincerity,

148
00:09:54,799 --> 00:09:56,519
so I hope you won't hide anything...

149
00:09:57,039 --> 00:09:58,039
from me.

150
00:09:58,519 --> 00:09:59,600
Tell me the truth.

151
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:07,638
Did I scare you?

152
00:10:07,639 --> 00:10:08,919
I'm just kidding.

153
00:10:10,679 --> 00:10:12,600
