155
00:10:14,919 --> 00:10:16,479
I'm still half asleep.

156
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:17,559
All right.

157
00:10:17,720 --> 00:10:19,090
I know you're still half asleep.

158
00:10:19,639 --> 00:10:21,879
I just wanted
to help you wake up faster.

159
00:10:22,519 --> 00:10:24,600
Well, please wish your grandma
a happy birthday for me.

160
00:10:27,210 --> 00:10:28,239
Bye.

161
00:10:28,240 --> 00:10:29,240
Bye.

162
00:10:41,679 --> 00:10:42,679
Babe.

163
00:10:43,720 --> 00:10:44,759
He Zhi Nan.

164
00:10:45,559 --> 00:10:46,638
Babe.

165
00:10:46,639 --> 00:10:47,720
He Zhi Nan.

166
00:10:49,919 --> 00:10:50,999
Slow down.

167
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:52,398
You can't stay here tonight.

168
00:10:52,399 --> 00:10:53,399
Yes, I understand.

169
00:10:53,400 --> 00:10:54,879
You can either go home
or go to a hotel.

170
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:56,440
Nan Nan, listen to me.

171
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:58,840
I understand what you mean.

172
00:10:59,080 --> 00:11:00,159
I have to face...

173
00:11:00,799 --> 00:11:02,039
my miserable life.

174
00:11:02,440 --> 00:11:04,120
I have to face my parents.

175
00:11:05,159 --> 00:11:06,559
