177
00:11:08,120 --> 00:11:09,159
That's more like it.

178
00:11:09,519 --> 00:11:11,120
Let's check out the mall
before I go home.

179
00:11:12,279 --> 00:11:13,320
I'm not going.

180
00:11:13,679 --> 00:11:15,158
Come on. It's still early.

181
00:11:15,159 --> 00:11:16,799
I'm not going.

182
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:18,000
Just for a while.

183
00:11:18,039 --> 00:11:19,799
Think of it as helping me
with some mental preparation.

184
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:21,038
Okay?

185
00:11:21,039 --> 00:11:23,799
- I'm not ready yet.
- Let go of my hand.

186
00:11:24,639 --> 00:11:25,840
I'm not ready yet.

187
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:31,879
Buy whatever you want.

188
00:11:35,279 --> 00:11:36,360
Upstairs.

189
00:11:36,480 --> 00:11:37,639
They have food upstairs.

190
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:39,559
Let's get something to eat
after this.

191
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:53,398
Let's check out this shop.

192
00:11:53,399 --> 00:11:54,399
Come on.

193
00:11:54,799 --> 00:11:55,840
- Welcome.
- Hello.

194
00:11:58,279 --> 00:11:59,320
What's wrong?

195
00:11:59,840 --> 00:12:00,840
Nothing.

196
00:12:04,519 --> 00:12:05,600
Their clothes are nice.

197
00:12:06,799 --> 00:12:08,199
There are no men's clothes here.

198
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:09,200
Why are we here?

199
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:10,440
Didn't you always say...

200
00:12:10,441 --> 00:12:12,319
you didn't have appropriate clothing
for the company's annual event?

201
00:12:12,320 --> 00:12:13,320
Take a look.

202
00:12:13,321 --> 00:12:14,559
I don't want to buy clothes anymore.

203
00:12:14,879 --> 00:12:16,320
We're already here. Take a look.

204
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:19,399
Hello, sir. How may I help you?

205
00:12:19,799 --> 00:12:21,600
Do you have
this year's new collection?

206
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:23,239
Yes, it's over there.
Let me show you.

207
00:12:23,240 --> 00:12:24,320
Okay.

208
00:12:27,559 --> 00:12:28,638
(I saw you with him!)

209
00:12:28,639 --> 00:12:32,519
(Nan Nan, I'm very sad.
Why did you lie to me?)

210
00:12:44,600 --> 00:12:46,679
Whatever happens will happen.

211
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:51,480
Nan Nan.

212
00:12:52,919 --> 00:12:54,000
What do you think of this?

213
00:12:55,039 --> 00:12:56,080
It's nice, right?

214
00:12:56,559 --> 00:12:57,600
Look at its design.

215
00:12:57,960 --> 00:12:59,559
And the pants too.

216
00:13:09,679 --> 00:13:10,679
Your phone is ringing.

217
00:13:11,799 --> 00:13:12,840
I'm going to try it on.

218
00:13:19,879 --> 00:13:20,919
Hello?

219
00:13:21,519 --> 00:13:23,000
You're with him, right?

220
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:25,960
Don't panic.

221
00:13:27,320 --> 00:13:28,399
Where are you?

222
00:13:31,879 --> 00:13:32,919
I saw him.

223
00:13:36,799 --> 00:13:37,879
What's done is done.

224
00:13:38,360 --> 00:13:39,600
Let's hear what he has to say.

225
00:13:41,360 --> 00:13:42,399
I miss you so much.

226
00:13:44,200 --> 00:13:45,919
I'm so jealous that I'm going crazy,

227
00:13:46,600 --> 00:13:47,879
but I still miss you so much.

228
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:50,360
I'll wait for you.

229
00:13:57,919 --> 00:13:59,000
I'll be right back.

230
00:13:59,600 --> 00:14:01,480
Okay, I'll wait for you.

231
00:14:02,399 --> 00:14:03,519
I won't bother you anymore.

232
00:14:11,320 --> 00:14:12,320
Don't just stand there.

233
00:14:12,840 --> 00:14:13,919
