- You're welcome.

237
00:14:35,559 --> 00:14:36,559
Why...

238
00:14:36,560 --> 00:14:37,600
Why aren't you wearing it?

239
00:14:38,399 --> 00:14:39,720
I don't want it.

240
00:14:40,120 --> 00:14:41,200
No.

241
00:14:41,240 --> 00:14:42,279
That shirt is pretty.

242
00:14:42,399 --> 00:14:43,558
- Try it on.
- That shirt...

243
00:14:43,559 --> 00:14:44,799
If you want to buy it,

244
00:14:45,200 --> 00:14:47,039
you'll have to spend
your parents' money.

245
00:14:49,360 --> 00:14:50,720
You're giving them
the silent treatment...

246
00:14:51,039 --> 00:14:52,320
while spending their money.

247
00:14:52,919 --> 00:14:55,120
How can you confidently announce
that you've grown up?

248
00:14:56,639 --> 00:14:58,039
- But I...
- Gao Peng.

249
00:14:58,480 --> 00:15:00,399
You can't avoid
what you have to deal with.

250
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:02,440
If you really want
to give me a gift,

251
00:15:02,720 --> 00:15:04,000
spend your own money.

252
00:15:06,639 --> 00:15:09,279
Go back and talk to your parents.

253
00:15:09,639 --> 00:15:10,679
Okay?

254
00:15:30,360 --> 00:15:31,798
Go back and talk to your parents.

255
00:15:31,799 --> 00:15:32,879
Take your time.

256
00:15:34,919 --> 00:15:35,960
Call me if you need anything.

257
00:15:36,759 --> 00:15:37,799
You too.

258
00:15:38,919 --> 00:15:39,960
Bye.

259
00:16:10,799 --> 00:16:11,799
How despicable.

260
00:16:12,360 --> 00:16:13,840
The worst part is that
you're actually enjoying it.

261
00:16:13,919 --> 00:16:15,158
Being liked by two people
at the same time...

262
00:16:15,159 --> 00:16:16,159
proves I'm attractive,

263
00:16:16,159 --> 00:16:17,159
so why can't I be happy?

264
00:16:17,639 --> 00:16:18,758
There's nothing wrong
with being pursued.

265
00:16:18,759 --> 00:16:20,119
But if you enjoy it,
you're being trashy.

266
00:16:20,120 --> 00:16:22,600
Lying to enjoy it
makes you even worse.

267
00:16:27,600 --> 00:16:31,440
(Shengyi Taxi)

268
00:17:03,799 --> 00:17:04,799
What's wrong?

269
00:17:04,839 --> 00:17:05,890
What are you thinking about?

270
00:17:07,359 --> 00:17:08,410
Nothing.

271
00:17:08,519 --> 00:17:09,558
I just think...

272
00:17:09,559 --> 00:17:10,890
that the past few days
have been so wonderful.

273
00:17:11,000 --> 00:17:12,359
It feels like a dream.

274
00:17:13,119 --> 00:17:15,000
I'll be back to reality soon.

275
00:17:17,359 --> 00:17:18,519
Silly girl.

276
00:17:23,079 --> 00:17:25,559
Currently,
the route ahead is congested.

277
00:17:25,890 --> 00:17:28,000
The estimated travel time
is 50 minutes.

278
00:17:28,480 --> 00:17:30,479
